headline: Record dengue outbreak in Americas kills 7,700 this year, PAHO says
summary: Reported cases of dengue in the Americas nearly tripled to a record high of over 12.6 million this year, including 21,000 severe cases and over 7,700 deaths, the Pan American Health Organization said...
